      "content": "Interesting. Thanks for the breakdown. \n\nCould you elaborate a bit more on why you think the university tier impacts their leadership potential? Specifically, why would a degree from Tsinghua or San Jose State affect their ability to lead teams in a US-based environment compared to an Ivy League grad?",
